creator: Blue Ghee
descriptionHtml:
Now you can, create unique stylish Name and Nickname for game profile, social media profile and other online platforms profile with ease.
Name and Nickname Generator (NNG) app help to create your own stylish looking Name and Nickname for your profile.

* Features on the app :

① Names for Boys and Girls.
→ This app shows 1000+ unique name for Boys and Girls. You can find best Name or Nickname which suits your character and profile with ease.

② Convert Name and Nickname to unique style.
→ You can convert your normal looking Name and Nickname to cool looking by changing it's style. By converting your Name and Nickname style your each character looks different when displayed on your online profiles.

③ Add symbols to the name.
→ You can add 1000+ Unicode symbols and generate new unique Name and Nickname for your online profiles.

* Symbols Category
☞ Premade Symbols (Pre.S)
☞ Miscellaneous Symbols (Mi.S)
☞ Miscellaneous Technical Symbols (Mi.T.S)
☞ Mathematical Symbols (Ma.S)
☞ Arrows Symbols(Arr)
☞ Number Forms Symbols(Nm.F.S)
☞ Letter Like Symbols (L.L.S)
☞ Currency Symbols (Cu.S)

④ Generate Nicknames
→ With the use of unique character style and symbols you will get unique Name and Nickname for your online profiles with ease.
